  "altLabel": "International Standard Name Identifier",
  "notation": "ISNI",
  "definition": "A 16-character identifier for the public identity of a person or organization, defined by ISO 27729 and assigned by the ISNI International Agency. When used as a funder identifier, the ISNI uniquely identifies the funding organization.",
